OL,4,COliver Campbell: Calls to review
OL,5,C30-year-old murder conviction
OL,6, A man with learning difficulties who
OL,7, admitted to a murder 30 years ago
OL,8, should have his conviction quashed
OL,9, because he confessed to police without
OL,10, a lawyer present, his solicitor says.
OL,12,FOliver Campbell's confession would be
OL,13,Fruled inadmissible today, Arthur
OL,14,FMullinger told BBC Newsnight.
OL,16,FCampbell, who was 19 at the time, says
OL,17,Fhe was "put under pressure" to "admit
OL,18,Fto something that I didn't do".
OL,20,FPolice say the interviews were fair,
OL,21,Fwhile a judge ruled them admissible.
